  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>The Arize Hotel is a Tourist, Family Style, City hotel, City apartment hotel. Located in City Centre - Sukhumvit Rd. area. Shopping is right next door and the nightlife/restaurants are right next to the hotel.</Text>
